      skos:note "Decision to publish liberally and not hold IP back. The moat is the transformation pipeline and the accumulated graph, not the ideas. Content posture: full tour of the castle — you could bring them everywhere except maybe the metaphorical security room, and even that you could probably show them the camera feeds. The line between what to publish and what not to publish is known and understood." ;
